  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Cardiovascular Disease
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Non-communicable
Symptoms:    Chest pain, shortness of breath
Treatment:   Statins, surgery, stents
Deaths/yr:   17.9M
Vaccine:     No (for most types)
Discovered:  Ancient

Disease:     Dengue
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Dengue virus
Transmission:Aedes mosquito
Symptoms:    Fever, severe joint pain, rash
Treatment:   Supportive care, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.04M
Vaccine:     Yes (for previously infected)
Discovered:  1779

Disease:     Hepatitis B
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HBV
Transmission:Blood, sexual contact
Symptoms:    Often asymptomatic; jaundice
Treatment:   Antivirals (tenofovir)
Deaths/yr:   0.82M
Vaccine:     Yes (highly effective)
Discovered:  1965

